quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  38,62,"Ɓeya mbi'i: "Ko haɗi men jiugol worɓe, ɓe min limtaynoo e boonɓe ɓen?"
  38,63,"Hara min njogitorno ɓe toon jalnori, kaa ko gite (amen) yawti ɓe?""
  38,64,"Pellet, ka goonga, ko ɗuum woni yeddondiral yimɓe Yiite ɓeen."
  38,65,"Maaku: "Anndee ko mi jeertinoowo. Deweteeɗo woo alaa, si wonaa Allah Gooto, pooluɗo On,"
  38,66,"Jeyɗo kammuuji ɗin e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde ɗin ɗiɗi, pooluɗo, kaforoowo On"."
  38,67,"Maaku: "(ndee Alqur'aanaare), ko nde kabaaru mawɗo,"
  38,68,"kono hoɗon ɗuurnii ɗum."
  38,69,"Ganndal alanaano kam, e fii mbatu ngun dowrowu, tuma nde ɓe weeñidaynoo."
  38,70,"Wahayinaaka e am, si wanaa won'de min on, ko mi jeertinoowo ɓanngina"."
  38,71,"Jaŋto nde Joomi maa daalannoo Malaa'ika'en: "Min mi tagiroowo ɓanndiŋke, immorde loopal."
  38,72,"si mi fotindirii mo, Mi wuttii e makko ruuhu am on, haray suuyanee mo cujjon"."
  38,73,"Malaa'ika'en fof cujji ɓe denndaangal."
  38,74,"si wonaa Ibuliisa, o mawnintinii, o woni jiyaaɗo e yedduɓe ɓen."
  38,75,"(Allah) daali: "eey ma yo Ibuliisa, ko haɗu maa sujjangol ko Mi tagiri juuɗe am? A mawnintini kaa a jeya e townitiiɓe ɓeen?""
  38,76,"O wi'i: "Ko min ɓuri mo moƴƴude. A tagirii lam e yiite, A tagirii mo kaŋko e loopal"."
  38,77,"O daali: "Yaltu ton, aan, ko a diiwaaɗo;"
  38,78,"pellet, kuddi sm ndin fawike ma haa Ñande njoɓdi diina"."
  38,79,"(Ibuliisa) wi'i : "Joomi am, neeɓnitanam, haa ñande nde ɓe immintintee"."
  38,80,"O daali: "A jeyaama e neeɓnitanteeɓe ɓen,"
  38,81,"haa e ñalaande happu ganndaaɗo"."
  38,82,"O wi'i: "Mi wooɗndirii mawngu maa ngun ! Ma mi bewnuɓe fof maɓɓe,"
  38,83,"si wonaa jiyaaɓe Maa, laɓɓinaaɓe ɓen e maɓɓe"."